LIBRARY PROJECT Environment setup

1. DATABASE:
    https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-mysql-on-ubuntu-20-04
    CREATE USER 'svc_jsotlibrary'@'%' IDENTIFIED BY 'Sam_12345';
    GRANT ALL ON *.* TO 'svc_jsotlibrary'@'%';
    NOTE: Remove line 'bind-address 127.0.0.1' from '/etc/mysql/mysql.conf.d/mysqld.cnf'
    sudo service mysql restart

2. API:
    sudo apt install openjdk-11-jdk

